title: Lectro Spektral Daze - Farther From Ordinary Reality
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

There is no better way to start this new year than to rejoice in this highly energetic, trippy and synthesizer-driven Goa trance album that will expand the talent and creativity of Lectro Spektral Daze even better. He put a lot of effort and creativity to extend his vision even further and the result is 6 new and previously unreleased tracks, including 2 amazing remixes by Neogoa finest - Lunar Dawn and JaraLuca. Download Full Fractal Vision - http://www.neogoa.net/full-fractal-vision/

Tracklist:

01 - Constant Awareness (145 BPM)
02 - Rave Drugs (145 BPM)
03 - Almond Eyes (145 BPM)
04 - Quite A Trip [JaraLuca Remix] (145 BPM)
05 - Farther From Ordinary Reality (145 BPM)
06 - Almost Nothing (145 BPM)
07 - Quite A Trip (145 BPM)
08 - Farther From Ordinary Reality [Lunar Dawn Remix] (145 BPM)

For more free Goa trance and ambient music, please visit us:
